snippet.title: Divorce Attorney Brian J. Kramer Interviewed about the Johnny Depp divorce settlement.
snippet.description: Beverly Hills Divorce Attorney was interviewed on August 16, 2016 by Inside Edition about the Johnny Depp and Amber Heard Divorce settlement.  In this interview, Brian explains one of the reasons why Johnny Depp likely agreed to this record breaking $7 million dollar settlement with actress Amber Heard.  Brian surmises that there was likely additional evidence demonstrating abusive conduct by Depp of Heard, which gave 7 million reasons for Mr. Depp to want a non-disclosure/confidentiality and gag order.
